snippet.title: Maya The Bee: Sweet Gold (GBA) World 1 (Hard Mode)
snippet.description:
Well, thanks to The Cutting Room Floor site, I now discovered about two GBA games based on the Maya The Bee Cartoon(the one before the CGI animated version), and I've been almost like playing the heck out of them, the sequel even more so.

Here I'm just doing a good ol' playthrough of Maya The Bee: Sweet Gold, on its Hard Mode setting(without any TAS stuff). Mistakes might happen throughout, due to the fact that I often stress while recording my videos (even if I don't need to).
